│ The correct approach, as identified in the root cause        │
│ analysis, is to handle the simplification correctly. The     │
│ original analysis suggested a fix that involved checking the │
│ return of `replaceInstUsesWith`. While that is a good        │
│ practice, the immediate problem is the `unreachable`. A      │
│ simpler fix is to handle all predicates.                     │
│                                                              │
