│ `canonicalizeICmpBool` but do it in a way that is compatible │
│ with its static nature. Instead of calling                   │
│ `replaceInstUsesWith`, which is an `InstCombinerImpl`        │
│ method, we can return the value that should replace the      │
│ instruction. The caller, `visitICmpInst`, will then perform  │
│ the replacement.                                             │
│                                                              │
