│ `Value*`) is not directly possible if it's not an            │
│ instruction.                                                 │
│                                                              │
│ The best place to handle this is in `visitICmpInst` itself,  │
│ before calling `canonicalizeICmpBool`. This avoids the scope │
│ issue with `replaceInstUsesWith` and allows for direct       │
│ replacement.                                                 │
